-- Former Bristol-Myers Executives Schiff and Lane Get Prosecution Deferred
-- David Voreacos
-- 2010-06-29T19:12:10Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-29/former-bristol-myers-executives-schiff-and-lane-get-prosecution-deferred.html

          
          
             Former Bristol-Myers Squibb Co.
executives Frederick S. Schiff and Richard Lane will have
federal criminal fraud charges dismissed in one year under an
agreement with the Justice Department.  
 To contact the reporter on this story:
